data.description: This well kept townhome in the full security community of DeCordova features vaulted ceilings with an open dining area and statement fireplace. The home has a split floor plan with the master bed and bath downstairs and the 2 additional rooms upstairs with a shared bathroom. Ample closet space and garage attic for storage. Covered patio and fenced backyard with minimal maintenance. The open concept kitchen features a built-in microwave, electric range, and Dishwasher. The large master bedroom contains its own bathroom with double sink, water closet, large tub and separate shower. Professional Photos will be uploaded Tuesday evening. Buyer and agent to verify all information.
